{"tid":1223411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】立法會大會會議議程 2019年6月19日 星期三 上午11時","createTime":"2019-06-14T16:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:58:56.000Z","uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4be20f536c4fb56a2ba211e9cfceed1b79069c","tid":1223411,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"I.提交本會省覽的文件<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>容後通知</strong></span>（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">高度危險的容後通知</span></strong>）<br />\nII.質詢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>容後通知</strong></span>（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">高度危險的容後通知</span></strong>）<br />\nIII.議員議案<br />\n1.&quot;加強打擊水貨活動，收緊內地居民來港的安排&quot;議案<br />\n林卓廷議員動議附錄1的議案<br />\n出席官員：有待政府當局通知<br />\n2.&quot;制訂輸入非本地培訓醫生的新機制&quot;議案<br />\n張宇人議員動議附錄2的議案<br />\n出席官員：有待政府當局通知<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/counmtg/agenda/cm20190619.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fagenda%2Fcm20190619.htm&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8JIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=150e3e26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/counmtg/agenda/cm20190619.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c87f9b798e25d5e06b10a27163ed69bc928a8a54","tid":1223411,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bc8691da628e49f53bf1e0de8d7e8007cd81e2","tid":1223411,"uid":256508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"星期一或二，大口狗隨時有會開。<br />\n保持警覺"},{"pid":"3f249b535fa8177a7976ca3fa59c6a54444e8870","tid":1223411,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42bc8691da628e49f53bf1e0de8d7e8007cd81e2","tid":1223411,"uid":256508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"星期一或二，大口狗隨時有會開。<br />\n保持警覺"},"citedBy"